{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.560", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.160", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.680", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In der ganzen Stadt ist Berlinale. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.520", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es werden die neuesten Filme gezeigt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.960", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nur hier im Deutschen Bundestag kommen Linke und Gr\u00fcne schon wieder mit den alten Kamellen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.040", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Erfolglose Antr\u00e4ge zum Lobbyregister haben sie schon mehrfach eingebracht: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.960", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in der 16., "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.280", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in der 17. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.320", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und auch in der letzten Wahlperiode. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.760", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und p\u00fcnktlich zum Beginn der neuen Spielzeit ist das Thema wieder da: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.920", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das Lobbyregister, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.760", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ein Evergreen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.800", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Lassen Sie uns ein paar Schlaglichter auf den konkreten Gesetzentwurf der Linken werfen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.600", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zitat:"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.400", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ohne eine gesetzliche Grundlage\u00a0\u2026 ist es nicht m\u00f6glich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.680", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den notwendigen Grad an Verbindlichkeit und Klarheit\u00a0\u2026 zu erreichen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.200", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.040", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "da w\u00e4re es nat\u00fcrlich toll, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.840", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn sich der richtige und hehre Grundsatz der Klarheit auch in Form und Inhalt Ihres Entwurfes widerspiegeln w\u00fcrde."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "72.440", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie aber stellen einen langen Katalog von registrierungspflichtigen Handlungen und Daten auf und h\u00e4ngen einen ebenso langen Ausnahmekatalog hintendran. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "72.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.200", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie sagen \u201eTransparenz\u201c, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.680", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber Sie schaffen noch mehr B\u00fcrokratie."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "81.080", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ihr wichtigster Punkt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "81.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "85.720", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Einrichtung eines Bundesbeauftragten f\u00fcr politische Interessenvertretung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "85.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "87.160", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die FDP lehnt es ab, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.360", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ohne Not noch eine steuerfinanzierte Beh\u00f6rde einzurichten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "92.320", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn es ein Sachproblem gibt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "92.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.320", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "kann es mit Sicherheit durch bestehende Institutionen gel\u00f6st werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "96.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.560", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die F\u00fchrung des \u00f6ffentlichen Verb\u00e4nderegisters hat die Bundestagsverwaltung jedenfalls bislang nicht in die Knie gezwungen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.080", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zu den Kosten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "111.800", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In den letzten Wochen haben viele vielfach das intensive Ringen der GroKo-Parteien um die Postenverteilung kritisiert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "111.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "115.200", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Viel eleganter ist da nat\u00fcrlich der hier aufgezeigte Weg, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "115.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.560", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "einfach ganz neue \u00c4mter zu schaffen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "122.640", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Gehalt des Beauftragten ist der einzige Punkt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "122.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "124.760", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zu dem Sie sich konkrete Gedanken gemacht haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "124.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.320", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was es denn kosten soll. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "128.760", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zu den Kosten f\u00fcr das Register selbst: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "128.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "130.640", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Schweigen im Walde! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "130.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.160", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das finde ich intransparent. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.360", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die W\u00e4hlerinnen und W\u00e4hler haben es verdient, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "138.360", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "von Ihnen zumindest eine ungef\u00e4hre Hausnummer zu h\u00f6ren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "138.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "142.960", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ihr Entwurf sieht besondere Ausnahmen von der Registerpflicht vor, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "142.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.320", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "etwa f\u00fcr Anw\u00e4ltinnen und Anw\u00e4lte bei der \u201eWahrnehmung oder Vertretung der rechtlichen Interessen \u2026 im Zusammenhang mit einem verwaltungsbeh\u00f6rdlichen oder gerichtlichen Verfahren\u201c. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.080", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das muss auch sein; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "155.640", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn sonst w\u00e4re ein Anwalt gezwungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "155.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "158.880", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nicht alle M\u00f6glichkeiten seines Mandates auszusch\u00f6pfen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "158.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.080", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "oder er m\u00fcsste sehenden Auges gegen die Vertraulichkeit des Mandates versto\u00dfen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.520", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Problem Ihres Vorschlags liegt in der Praxis: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "173.040", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie soll man die politische Interessenvertretung trenngenau von der rechtlichen Interessenvertretung abgrenzen? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "173.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.520", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielleicht ist das der Grund, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.760", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "warum in \u00d6sterreich Anw\u00e4lte gleich ganz von der Registerpflicht ausgenommen sind."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.280", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zur legislativen Fu\u00dfspur: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "182.520", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Bundesministerium der Justiz\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "182.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "182.680", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das ist nicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "182.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "183.000", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie es in Ihrer Begr\u00fcndung steht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "183.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "184.880", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das \u201eBundesministerium f\u00fcr Recht\u201c\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "184.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "192.840", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und f\u00fcr Verbraucherschutz ver\u00f6ffentlicht schon jetzt freiwillig die zu einem Gesetzesvorhaben eingegangenen Stellungnahmen auf seiner Homepage. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "192.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "196.200", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das scheint in der Sache also kein gro\u00dfes Problem zu sein. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "196.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.720", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich frage mich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.320", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob es Ihnen vielleicht nur um den Showeffekt geht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "203.880", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn Sie ein funktionierendes Prozedere gesetzlich regeln wollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "203.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "206.800", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nur damit am Ende das Gleiche dabei herumkommt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "206.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.760", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was wir jetzt schon auf freiwilliger Basis haben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.120", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Klare Vorstellungen haben Sie zum Bestrafen von Verst\u00f6\u00dfen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.720", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie finden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "221.200", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bis zu 10\u00a0Prozent des Gesamtumsatzes eines Gesch\u00e4ftsjahres sind f\u00fcr ein Unternehmen nicht zu viel. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "221.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "224.080", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Transparenz ist ein wichtiger Grundsatz im Rechtsstaat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "224.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.600", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Verh\u00e4ltnism\u00e4\u00dfigkeit ist aber auch einer."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "230.280", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ihr Entwurf zeigt vor allem, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "230.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "235.800", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie viel Abneigung die Schim\u00e4re einer vermeintlichen Lobbyistenrepublik in Ihnen hervorruft. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "235.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "238.560", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kernaussage Ihres Entwurfs ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "238.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "242.360", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es bei denen im Bundestag nicht mit rechten Dingen zugeht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "242.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "243.720", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass nicht die Bundesregierung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "243.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "246.400", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern eine Lobbying\u00adindustrie das Land regiert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "246.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "249.440", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass man den Abgeordneten stets auf die Finger schauen muss, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "249.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "251.400", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damit sie nicht das Kungeln anfangen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "251.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "257.480", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch dieses plakative Anklagen vermeintlich schlimmer Zust\u00e4nde tr\u00e4gt zur Politikverachtung bei. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "257.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "258.120", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich bitte Sie, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "258.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "259.240", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das zu bedenken. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "259.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "261.080", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Drau\u00dfen mag Berlinale sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "261.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "263.040", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber hier sind wir nicht im Kino."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "263.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "266.920", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Noch ein kurzer Hinweis an die lieben Kollegen von der AfD: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "266.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "268.760", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich finde es bemerkenswert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "268.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "270.040", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Sie sich jetzt auf einmal, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "270.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "271.720", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wo es Ihnen passt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "271.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "272.840", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "des Grundgesetzes annehmen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "272.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "275.280", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ansonsten scheinen Sie es v\u00f6llig zu ignorieren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "275.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "277.080", 
